    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>This references two new parameters - <code>facebook_app_id</code> and <code>facebook_app_secret</code>.
Add these to your <code>parameters.yml</code> (and <code>parameters.yml.dist</code>) file with your Facebook
application's "App ID" and "App Secret" values:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="01b69ed14c">
