</div><h2 id="creating-the-facebookconnectcontroller">Creating the FacebookConnectController <a class="headerlink" href="social-login#creating-the-facebookconnectcontroller" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Don't think about security yet! Instead, look at the flow above. We'll need a controller
with <em>two</em> actions: one that simply redirects to Facebook for authorization (<code>/connect/facebook</code>)
and another that handles what happens when Facebook redirects back to us (<code>/connect/facebook-check</code>):</p>
