<h2 id="filling-in-the-authenticator-methods">Filling in the Authenticator Methods <a class="headerlink" href="social-login#filling-in-the-authenticator-methods" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Your authenticator is now being used by Symfony. So let's fill in each method:</p>
